    "description": "Tsuji Hongo IT Consulting Co.,Ltd. develops a digital transformation platform designed to provide specialized know-how for better decision-making in the areas of corporate operations, inheritance tax, and accounting practices. It provides consulting services including business visualization, business improvement, early monthly settlement, strengthening of internal controls, management accounting support, and standardization of accounting operations; and technology which provides support in proposing and implementing the optimal system and promote business transformation through the power of technology, including software and hardware sales agency. It also provides operation outsourcing services, from system setup services to back-office operations such as bookkeeping, payroll, and other accounting support such as invoice issuance. The company also offers development and operation of web services for accounting firms and SaaS based accounting/HR operation and dispatching specialist personnel. The company was incorporated in 2012 and is based in Shibuya, Japan. Tsuji Hongo IT Consulting Co.,Ltd. operates as a subsidiary of Hongo Holdings Co., Ltd."
